43:09.360 --> 43:10.200
OK, I'm sorry.

43:12.120 --> 43:15.680
Always with you.
That was the deal. To share everything.

43:15.760 --> 43:17.720
Carla, really, it was nothing.

43:17.800 --> 43:19.360
It was nothing!

43:20.640 --> 43:21.880
Come, give me a hug.

43:24.400 --> 43:26.240
-Carla, I didn't even like it.
-This...

43:26.800 --> 43:30.040
was something we did to avoid infidelity,
lies.

43:30.600 --> 43:33.120
To revive a relationship that was dead.

43:34.320 --> 43:37.680
But given all this,
it's better if it remains buried.

43:49.120 --> 43:50.440
-Hello.
-Hi.

43:53.400 --> 43:55.040
-Let's go.
-No.

44:00.720 --> 44:02.120
One fifty, please.

44:11.240 --> 44:12.080
I need change.

44:19.280 --> 44:21.880
-Why don't you answer my texts?
-I no longer have a cell.

44:21.960 --> 44:25.960
-And when can we meet?
-I'll be behind this counter for 2 years.

44:26.720 --> 44:28.440
-Omar.
-What are you doing?

44:30.920 --> 44:31.760
Thanks.

44:44.680 --> 44:45.560
Omar, please.

44:48.080 --> 44:48.920
Please.

44:49.000 --> 44:49.880
I can't.

44:54.320 --> 44:55.160
Have a good day.

44:57.080 --> 44:57.960
Bye.

45:16.000 --> 45:17.480
Do you want to know whose it is?

45:18.560 --> 45:20.960
-Do you really need to know?
-No. Marina.

45:21.160 --> 45:22.040
Enough.

45:22.120 --> 45:23.320
I'm tired.

45:24.640 --> 45:26.360
I'm tired of chasing after you.

45:26.440 --> 45:27.920
-Maybe--
-Listen to me! Please.

45:28.000 --> 45:31.200
I'm tired of trying all the time
to convince you about us.

45:31.480 --> 45:34.120
But most of all,
I'm tired of waiting for you to find...

45:34.200 --> 45:36.840
the fucking courage to break up with me!

45:38.600 --> 45:39.640
Samuel.

45:41.880 --> 45:45.280
How would you have reacted
if she had decided to end it with you?

45:45.920 --> 45:48.080
I don't know, because that never happened.

45:57.400 --> 45:59.400
I have never seen this message.

45:59.920 --> 46:00.840
She wrote it.

46:02.320 --> 46:04.640
She never hit the send button.

46:05.320 --> 46:06.560
Read it, please.

46:09.200 --> 46:10.040
"Nano,

46:11.480 --> 46:12.400
forgive me,

46:15.480 --> 46:17.000
but I can't do this.

46:18.080 --> 46:19.560
I can't leave, I'm sorry."

46:20.880 --> 46:22.640
Why didn't she tell you in person?

46:23.440 --> 46:25.640
Was she afraid you might react violently?

46:39.520 --> 46:41.840
Still thinking about the blackmail idea?

46:44.240 --> 46:45.160
I'm not sure.

47:00.760 --> 47:02.320
What are you thinking?

47:04.360 --> 47:05.440
Let's go get them.

48:28.560 --> 48:29.480
Subtitle translation
by Soledad Etchemandy-Blankenship
